{"word":"κρυερός","slug":"κρυερός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κρυερός</b></el> <el>(κρυερός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κρύος'><el>κρύος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>icy, chilling</i>, in <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b> only <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>κρυεροῖο γόοιο, κρυεροῖο φόβοιο</el>; so <el>κρυερὰ πάθεα</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>icy-cold</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}